  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 0.86,
      "text": "Now, look at code."
    },
    {
      "start": 1.94,
      "end": 4.86,
      "text": "For 50 years, generating new code was expensive."
    },
    {
      "start": 5.44,
      "end": 8.44,
      "text": "Writing from scratch took hours, days, weeks."
    },
    {
      "start": 9.0,
      "end": 11.06,
      "text": "So when something broke, you patched."
    },
    {
      "start": 11.22,
      "end": 12.22,
      "text": "Of course, you patched."
    },
    {
      "start": 12.42,
      "end": 13.12,
      "text": "It was rational."
    },
    {
      "start": 14.8,
      "end": 16.88,
      "text": "Now, here's where it gets interesting."
    },
    {
      "start": 17.5,
      "end": 19.38,
      "text": "AI made patching faster, too."
    },
    {
      "start": 19.98,
      "end": 22.56,
      "text": "Cursor, Claude code, co-pilot."
    },
    {
      "start": 23.08,
      "end": 24.52,
      "text": "They're incredible tools."
    },
    {
      "start": 25.08,
      "end": 26.52,
      "text": "They understand your code base."
    },
    {
      "start": 26.52,
      "end": 27.82,
      "text": "Suggest fixes?"
    },
    {
      "start": 28.46,
      "end": 30.1,
      "text": "Catch bugs before you make them."
    },
    {
      "start": 31.26,
      "end": 33.68,
      "text": "Look, each patch is getting faster."
    },
    {
      "start": 34.12,
      "end": 34.72,
      "text": "That's real."
    },
    {
      "start": 35.24,
      "end": 37.66,
      "text": "That's what you feel when you use these tools."
    },
    {
      "start": 39.24,
      "end": 41.98,
      "text": "But watch the dashed line, the total cost."
    },
    {
      "start": 42.56,
      "end": 43.52,
      "text": "It's barely moving."
    },
    {
      "start": 44.24,
      "end": 46.44,
      "text": "Because even though each patch is faster,"
    },
    {
      "start": 47.1,
      "end": 48.74,
      "text": "every patch still leaves residue."
    },
    {
      "start": 49.36,
      "end": 51.6,
      "text": "Technical debt, and that debt accumulates."
    },
    {
      "start": 52.36,
      "end": 54.84,
      "text": "Faster now, because you're patching faster."
    },
    {
      "start": 56.52,
      "end": 59.96,
      "text": "AI gave you a 60% speed up on individual patches."
    },
    {
      "start": 60.54,
      "end": 61.52,
      "text": "But your total cost?"
    },
    {
      "start": 62.18,
      "end": 64.88,
      "text": "Down 4%, the debt ate the rest."
    }
  ]
}